reviews.review_text: This may have nothing to do with this McDonald s but I was hoping to get some help from you. I got a parking ticket from this McDonalds parking lot while eating at this McDonalds yesterday. I parked the car and went into the store from the main entrance (not the small entrance thats next to the parking lot) because my friend was waiting for me at that door. I tried to dispute the parking ticket with Royal Parkings and explained the situation, even attached my receipt. The appeal department replied and said as long as I left the parking lot Id need to pay for the ticket. I actually walked straight to the restaurant and spent an hour in there with food and drinks from McDonalds, but still need to pay for the ticket just because I went through a different door? This is not the right thing to do to people in my opinion. McDonald s should have a talk to their service providers when they act like a scammer.

This McDonalds is always a treat. The staff are all very friendly and you get the standard McDonalds taste we all expect.....but theres more. Pre-Pandemic Id go in on a Friday night just to see the equivalent of a performance art production. New Years Eve (in years without a global pandemic) is truly a spectacular event with 100s of drunk youngster (of age presumably) getting their McD****s fix. If you visit and you get poor service or they mess up your order dont sweat it. Its a small price to pay for a uniquely bustling experience!

.Hey beautiful, so here it is the time of year again when we try to raise awareness of breast cancer through a game. Its very easy and I was hoping you would participate. Last year we had to write colour of our bras on our status. Men wondered for days whether what was going on with random colours on status. This year we make reference to our love life status as a flavour. Dont answer to this message just post corresponding word on your status and send this message privately to all the girls in your friend list. Blueberry-single. Pineapple-its complicated. Raspberry-I dont want to commit. Apple-engaged. Cherry-relationship. Banana-married. Avocado-Im the better half. Strawberry-Cant find Mr. Right. Lemon-I want to be single. Raisin-I want to get married to my partner. Last time the bra game was mentioned on TV. Lets see if we can get there with this one. Please resend this to all your girl friends and update your status.
